A

arrayAgg(Field<T>) - Static method in class com.bendb.dropwizard.jooq.PostgresSupport
Applies the array_agg aggregate function on a field, resulting in the input values being concatenated into an array.
arrayAggNoNulls(Field<T>) - Static method in class com.bendb.dropwizard.jooq.PostgresSupport
Like PostgresSupport.arrayAgg(org.jooq.Field<T>), but uses array_remove to eliminate SQL NULL values from the result.
